     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts mappingmodelemetierCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"mappingmodelemetierCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"hcmappingmodelemetierCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Groupe 1 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-entete-document</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-clinical-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.identifiantUniqueDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.id</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.modeleDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.templateId</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.typeDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.titreDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.title</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.dateDeCreationDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.effectiveTime</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.niveauConfidentialiteDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.confidentialityCode</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.languePrincipaleDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.languageCode</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.identifiantLotDeVersionsDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.setId</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.versionDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.versionNumber</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.StatutDocument</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.documentationOf.serviceEvent.lab:statusCode</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.patient</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.recordTarget</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.auteur</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.author</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.operateurSaisie</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>ClinicalDocument.dataEnterer</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEnteteDocument.informateur</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.ht